Please give Nic
all my love, and...

33:40.135 --> 33:41.560
tell her I'm sorry
I couldn't stay.

33:42.971 --> 33:45.188
How is your mom doing?

33:46.233 --> 33:49.526
They were married 41 years.

33:49.677 --> 33:52.863
An arranged marriage
that worked, you know?

33:53.014 --> 33:55.949
This is the only thing
that could've separated them.

33:59.729 --> 34:02.039
Yeah.

34:02.232 --> 34:04.190
I have to go.
Got to catch my plane.

34:04.293 --> 34:05.600
