<i> Dr. Pravesh, your father's</i>
<i> respiratory failure</i>

41:19.352 --> 41:20.368
<i> is getting worse.</i>

41:20.386 --> 41:21.961
<i> We need to intubate him.</i>

41:22.022 --> 41:23.480
<i> DEVON (over video):</i>
<i> What's the prognosis?</i>

41:23.673 --> 41:24.814
<i>DOCTOR:</i>
<i>We are doing everything we can,</i>

41:25.007 --> 41:27.150
<i> but he's very sick.</i>

41:27.301 --> 41:29.819
<i> DEVON:</i>
<i> Uh, I need to speak to him</i>
<i> before you intubate, please.</i>

41:30.012 --> 41:31.136
<i> DOCTOR:</i>
<i> Yes, of course.</i>

41:31.156 --> 41:33.156
<i> (Tejan coughing)</i>

41:37.019 --> 41:40.038
<i> -(strained breathing)</i>
<i> -DEVON: Dad, can you hear me?</i>

41:42.167 --> 41:43.983
<i> Dad, hang on.</i>

41:44.002 --> 41:45.651
<i> They're gonna intubate,</i>
<i> but don't give up.</i>

41:45.712 --> 41:47.895
<i> Keep fighting.</i>

41:47.956 --> 41:49.247
<i> People recover from this.</i>

41:49.341 --> 41:51.566
<i> People just like you. You...</i>

41:51.584 --> 41:55.011
<i> You can make it, you just...</i>
<i> you just got to fight.</i>

41:58.466 --> 41:59.999
<i> So proud of you, Devon.</i>

42:00.060 --> 42:01.726
<i> (coughing)</i>

42:04.005 --> 42:06.748
<i> Take care of your mom.</i>

42:06.808 --> 42:09.567
<i> DEVON:</i>
<i> I will take care of Mom,</i>
<i> no matter what. I promise.</i>

42:11.363 --> 42:15.031
<i> Dad, listen to me.</i>

42:16.034 --> 42:19.184
<i>I would be nothing without you.</i>

42:19.246 --> 42:21.095
<i> You helped put me</i>
<i> through medical school,</i>

42:21.114 --> 42:24.374
<i> driving nights and weekends,</i>
<i> working overtime.</i>

42:24.525 --> 42:28.603
<i> I believed in myself</i>
<i> because you believed in me.</i>

42:28.621 --> 42:31.047
<i> And I always knew, no matter</i>
<i> what, that you loved me.</i>

42:31.240 --> 42:35.218
<i> You are... everything.</i>

42:37.747 --> 42:39.514
<i> Dad?</i>

42:41.226 --> 42:43.785
<i> Dad?</i>

42:43.845 --> 42:45.711
<i> Can you hear me?</i>

42:45.772 --> 42:48.289
<i> Can you hear me? Dad?</i>

42:48.349 --> 42:51.359
<i> Dad, can you hear me?</i>

42:57.659 --> 42:58.741
(exhales)

43:00.770 --> 43:02.745
I love you, Dad.

